# Build artifacts the web build never reads and which break the CLI uploader.
# infra/cdk/cdk.out accumulates dozens of full-repo asset copies from `cdk deploy`
# (20k+ files), which blew past Vercel's 15k-file upload limit on manual deploys.
#
# NOTE: do NOT exclude workspace member dirs themselves (apps/*, packages/*,
# infra/cdk) — `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` needs every package.json the
# lockfile references. Only artifact subtrees are listed here.
**/cdk.out/
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
.git/
